<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ق ذ ر:</span> <span class="c2">(الْقَذَرُ)</span> ضِدُّ النَّظَافَةِ وَشَيْءٌ <span class="c2">(قَذِرٌ)</span> بَيِّنُ <span class="c2">(الْقَذَارَةِ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(قَذِرْتُ)</span> الشَّيْءَ مِنْ بَابِ طَرِبَ وَ <span class="c2">(تَقَذَّرْتُهُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(اسْتَقْذَرْتُهُ)</span> أَيْ كَرِهْتُهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>